223
00:30:21,987 --> 00:30:22,821
Ayo!

224
00:30:22,904 --> 00:30:24,448
Jalan!

225
00:30:24,531 --> 00:30:26,241
Berangkat!

226
00:30:39,004 --> 00:30:40,756
Ini jejak harimau.

227
00:30:46,845 --> 00:30:48,138
Namun, ada yang aneh.

228
00:30:49,264 --> 00:30:52,893
Biasanya harimau jalan ke arah berlawanan
karena benci suara besi,

229
00:30:52,976 --> 00:30:54,102
tapi kali ini tidak.

230
00:30:55,020 --> 00:30:56,271
Apa maksudmu?

231
00:30:57,564 --> 00:30:59,274
Ia sedang mendekati pemburu.

232
00:32:49,759 --> 00:32:50,886
Ini ulah harimau.

233
00:32:51,720 --> 00:32:54,431
Bukan harimau…

234
00:33:00,896 --> 00:33:02,856
Ini ulah monster.

235
00:33:09,321 --> 00:33:11,072
Minta para pemburu mundur.

236
00:33:11,865 --> 00:33:13,450
Kini kita yang turun tangan.

237
00:33:19,456 --> 00:33:21,458
Mundur!

238
00:33:22,292 --> 00:33:24,628
- Bergegaslah!
- Mundur!

239
00:34:23,395 --> 00:34:24,771
Itu orang Pajeowi. Adanglah!

240
00:35:37,093 --> 00:35:37,927
Tuan!

241
00:36:52,460 --> 00:36:53,962
Aneh.

242
00:36:54,838 --> 00:36:55,839
Itu harimau mati.

243
00:36:57,173 --> 00:36:58,550
Bagaimana mungkin?

244
00:37:15,400 --> 00:37:17,068
Ada yang lebih aneh.

245
00:37:17,152 --> 00:37:20,155
Jelas-jelas kami dengar
saudara kami tewas diterkam harimau.

246
00:37:20,238 --> 00:37:23,783
Lantas, di mana jasad saudara kami?

247
00:37:25,118 --> 00:37:27,328
Mereka masuk ke Pyesa-gun
yang secara hukum,

248
00:37:27,412 --> 00:37:28,830
dilarang dikunjungi.

249
00:37:28,913 --> 00:37:32,500
Kami tidak bertanggung jawab
atas kematian mereka.

250
00:37:34,419 --> 00:37:36,671
Saudara-saudara kami tewas
di tanah Joseon.

251
00:37:38,673 --> 00:37:41,176
Balas dendam akan segera dimulai.

252
00:38:31,059 --> 00:38:31,893
Ashin?

253
00:38:56,167 --> 00:38:58,294
Serang!

254
00:41:59,934 --> 00:42:05,440
KAMP MILITER JOSEON, CHUPAJIN

255
00:42:34,218 --> 00:42:37,388
Aku sudah menerima laporan
kematian misterius di desa perbatasan.

256
00:42:38,056 --> 00:42:39,849
Apa hanya kau yang tersisa?

257
00:42:42,143 --> 00:42:44,771
Bagaimana dengan ayahmu?

258
00:42:56,115 --> 00:42:57,700
Kudengar orang Pajeowi…

259
00:43:01,829 --> 00:43:04,916
membunuh seorang mata-mata dari Joseon.

260
00:43:06,375 --> 00:43:09,128
Apa kau menyeberangi sungai sendirian?

261
00:43:10,671 --> 00:43:12,381
Aku tak mengerti.

262
00:43:17,178 --> 00:43:19,305
Mengapa Pajeowi
bersikap begini kepada kami.

263
00:43:23,142 --> 00:43:26,062
Sekeras apa pun kupikirkan,
aku tetap tidak mengerti.

264
00:43:27,939 --> 00:43:30,817
Apa kau menemuiku
untuk mencari tahu alasan itu?

265
00:43:32,443 --> 00:43:33,444
Tidak.

266
00:43:37,281 --> 00:43:39,116
Itu tidak penting.

267
00:43:42,537 --> 00:43:45,331
Tolong balaskan dendam ayahku.

268
00:43:47,959 --> 00:43:50,294
Orang rendahan sepertiku
mustahil melakukannya,

269
00:43:52,046 --> 00:43:54,173
tapi Joseon adalah negara kuat.

270
00:43:54,257 --> 00:43:56,217
Pasti bisa menghukum mereka.

271
00:43:56,300 --> 00:43:58,010
Aku turut berduka,

272
00:43:58,636 --> 00:44:02,140
tapi ini bukan urusan Joseon.

273
00:44:02,223 --> 00:44:03,224
Ayahku…

274
00:44:05,184 --> 00:44:07,436
begitu setia pada Joseon.

275
00:44:12,692 --> 00:44:15,736
Walau tak bisa memberikan jabatan
kepada ayahku…

276
00:44:17,905 --> 00:44:20,032
kau pasti bisa
membalaskan dendamnya, 'kan?

277
00:44:22,368 --> 00:44:24,370
Tidak perlu terburu-buru.

278
00:44:24,912 --> 00:44:27,790
Tahun depan, tiga tahun lagi… Tidak.

279
00:44:29,000 --> 00:44:30,835
Sepuluh atau 20 tahun lagi pun tak apa.

280
00:44:35,798 --> 00:44:38,509
Selama kau bisa membuat mereka
menangis darah,

281
00:44:41,721 --> 00:44:43,347
aku sudah puas.

282
00:44:44,557 --> 00:44:46,184
Apa pun akan kulakukan.

283
00:44:46,767 --> 00:44:48,769
Bila perlu, aku bersedia

284
00:44:49,270 --> 00:44:51,439
menjadi mata-mata, atau jagal.

285
00:44:54,567 --> 00:44:58,195
Pekerjaan yang lebih berbahaya
atau hina pun tidak masalah.

286
00:45:04,702 --> 00:45:07,997
Tolong balaskan dendam ayahku.

287
00:45:12,501 --> 00:45:14,003
Bawa anak ini.

288
00:45:30,937 --> 00:45:32,438
Pakaiannya seperti Suku Jurchen.

289
00:45:37,944 --> 00:45:39,654
Kau akan tinggal di sini.

290
00:48:40,751 --> 00:48:42,294
Kudengar dia penyintas
dari desa perbatasan.

291
00:48:43,170 --> 00:48:44,588
Dasar bengis!

292
00:48:45,506 --> 00:48:47,675
Kabarnya dia mengubur
semua mayat sendirian.

293
00:49:12,700 --> 00:49:15,494
KAMP MILITER PAJEOWI

294
00:50:30,861 --> 00:50:31,987
- Hei.
- Apa?

295
00:50:32,071 --> 00:50:33,197
Lihat apa?

296
00:51:11,860 --> 00:51:12,778
Ashin.

297
00:51:19,493 --> 00:51:20,536
Keluar.

298
00:51:24,790 --> 00:51:25,791
Kau pikir

299
00:51:27,251 --> 00:51:28,752
kau akan bisa selamat…

300
00:51:31,839 --> 00:51:33,632
setelah membunuh tentara Joseon?

301
00:51:50,024 --> 00:51:51,942
Kau sudah dewasa. Pasti tak muat di sini.

302
00:52:51,794 --> 00:52:52,920
Kerja bagus.

303
00:53:11,980 --> 00:53:13,941
PEMBAWA PESAN

304
00:53:14,525 --> 00:53:15,901
Ada kabar penting!

305
00:53:15,984 --> 00:53:18,404
Konferensi perdamaian
dengan Jepang putus, katamu?

306
00:53:18,487 --> 00:53:19,613
Benar.

307
00:53:19,696 --> 00:53:21,573
Yang Mulia menitahkan
untuk membantu pertahanan di selatan,

308
00:53:21,657 --> 00:53:24,076
dan menyisakan prajurit
di Uiju dan Kanggye.

309
00:53:34,753 --> 00:53:37,840
Tinggalkan beberapa prajurit di sini
dan bersiap bertempur.

310
00:53:37,923 --> 00:53:38,882
Baik.

311
00:53:38,966 --> 00:53:43,178
Jangan sampai
kita kehilangan jejak Pajeowi.

312
00:53:43,262 --> 00:53:44,513
Baik, Tuan.

313
00:53:49,351 --> 00:53:50,352
Tuan!

314
00:53:51,019 --> 00:53:52,729
Apa-apaan ini?

315
00:53:53,814 --> 00:53:55,023
Aku pantas mati.

316
00:53:55,107 --> 00:53:57,317
Bila hal semacam ini kembali terjadi,

317
00:53:58,277 --> 00:54:00,154
tamatlah riwayatmu.

318
00:54:00,946 --> 00:54:02,281
Akan kuingat baik-baik.

319
00:54:15,836 --> 00:54:17,671
Kau harus menyeberangi sungai.

320
00:54:18,255 --> 00:54:21,675
Amatilah pergerakan Pajeowi
dengan lebih terperinci.

321
00:54:33,145 --> 00:54:37,483
MARKAS BESAR MILITER PAJEOWI

322
00:56:11,243 --> 00:56:12,619
Buka mulutmu.

323
00:56:13,954 --> 00:56:16,123
Buka mulutmu.

324
00:56:16,623 --> 00:56:18,333
Kau akan berumur panjang.

325
00:57:45,754 --> 00:57:48,632
MATA-MATA
YANG MENGKHIANATI SUKU SENDIRI

326
00:57:57,474 --> 00:57:58,558
Ayah…

327
00:58:06,733 --> 00:58:08,276
Ini aku, Ayah…

328
00:58:12,739 --> 00:58:13,907
Ayah…

329
00:58:17,869 --> 00:58:20,288
Ini aku, Ayah…

330
00:58:36,596 --> 00:58:38,181
Tolong…

331
00:58:38,849 --> 00:58:40,267
bunuh aku…

332
00:58:41,393 --> 00:58:42,644
Ayah.

333
00:58:42,728 --> 00:58:44,938
Ayah, mari…

334
00:58:45,856 --> 00:58:47,649
Mari kita pulang!

335
00:58:48,442 --> 00:58:49,651
Tak apa-apa.

336
00:58:50,485 --> 00:58:53,280
Semua baik-baik saja.
Mari kita pulang sekarang.

337
00:58:53,905 --> 00:58:55,449
Mari kita pulang!

338
00:58:57,200 --> 00:58:58,660
Bunuh aku…

339
00:59:02,664 --> 00:59:03,665
Tolong…

340
00:59:13,592 --> 00:59:14,760
Bunuh aku.

341
00:59:39,701 --> 00:59:41,203
Mari kita pulang.

342
00:59:57,219 --> 00:59:58,386
Tolong…

343
00:59:59,971 --> 01:00:01,181
bunuh aku,

344
01:00:02,307 --> 01:00:03,558
Ashin.

345
01:00:07,104 --> 01:00:08,480
Ashin…

346
01:02:09,226 --> 01:02:13,480
KANTOR KOMANDAN, CHUPAJIN

347
01:02:23,782 --> 01:02:24,616
Ashin?

348
01:02:49,307 --> 01:02:54,104
<i>Jurchen Pajeowi mengidamkan ginseng
dan menyusup ke Pyesa-gun,</i>

349
01:02:54,187 --> 01:02:56,564
<i>lalu diserang dan dibunuh.</i>

350
01:02:57,983 --> 01:03:02,904
<i>Peperangan dengan Jurchen Pajeowi
nyaris pecah akibat suasana kacau,</i>

351
01:03:02,988 --> 01:03:05,991
<i>tapi masalah selesai
dengan mengorbankan seseorang</i>

352
01:03:06,074 --> 01:03:08,326
<i>dari desa orang-orang barbar hina.</i>

353
01:03:11,496 --> 01:03:13,707
<i>Saudara-saudara kami tewas
di tanah Joseon.</i>

354
01:03:14,457 --> 01:03:17,043
Balas dendam akan segera dimulai.

355
01:03:23,466 --> 01:03:24,592
Berhenti!

356
01:03:32,976 --> 01:03:34,519
Percuma membunuh kami,

357
01:03:34,602 --> 01:03:36,104
sebab saudara lain pasti datang.

358
01:03:37,397 --> 01:03:39,190
Maka, korban jiwa semakin banyak.

359
01:03:39,274 --> 01:03:40,775
Kau benar.

360
01:03:41,443 --> 01:03:44,070
Saudara kalian bukan dibunuh harimau,

361
01:03:44,154 --> 01:03:45,905
melainkan diserang seseorang.

362
01:03:51,369 --> 01:03:53,621
Di tempat saudara kalian tewas,

363
01:03:54,539 --> 01:03:55,999
ada ini.

364
01:04:19,773 --> 01:04:23,902
<i>Apa kau menemuiku
untuk mencari tahu alasan itu?</i>

365
01:04:24,527 --> 01:04:27,655
Tolong balaskan dendam ayahku.

366
01:04:59,521 --> 01:05:01,398
Tolong jaga keluarga selama ayah tak ada.

367
01:05:40,979 --> 01:05:41,855
Ashin.

368
01:05:43,731 --> 01:05:44,607
Ashin.

369
01:05:54,492 --> 01:05:55,952
Bunga apa ini?

370
01:06:40,455 --> 01:06:41,498
Apa itu?

371
01:06:42,081 --> 01:06:42,957
Entahlah.

372
01:07:23,289 --> 01:07:25,208
Ada apa ini? Apa yang kau lakukan?

373
01:07:25,291 --> 01:07:27,418
Tolong! Tolong aku!

374
01:08:23,349 --> 01:08:24,726
Apa-apaan?

375
01:08:29,188 --> 01:08:30,857
Astaga, dinginnya!

376
01:08:37,739 --> 01:08:38,906
Dingin sekali.

377
01:08:58,801 --> 01:08:59,802
Dia sudah mati?

378
01:09:00,386 --> 01:09:01,304
Tunggu…

379
01:09:06,142 --> 01:09:07,143
Apa ini…

380
01:09:28,539 --> 01:09:30,291
Lepaskan!

381
01:13:37,038 --> 01:13:39,498
Tutup pintunya! Cepat!

382
01:14:02,021 --> 01:14:03,064
Dia sudah mati?

383
01:14:03,147 --> 01:14:03,981
Apa itu?

384
01:14:54,990 --> 01:14:56,742
Tidak! Jangan bunuh aku!

385
01:16:40,054 --> 01:16:41,055
Ashin…

386
01:16:52,233 --> 01:16:54,985
Tolong aku, Ashin.

387
01:17:07,873 --> 01:17:09,083
Tidak…

388
01:17:09,166 --> 01:17:11,460
Ashin! Apa yang kau lakukan?

389
01:17:11,544 --> 01:17:13,796
Tidak! Jangan bunuh aku!

390
01:17:13,879 --> 01:17:14,713
Ashin!

391
01:19:40,734 --> 01:19:41,735
Ashin.

392
01:19:43,320 --> 01:19:44,321
Jangan bunuh aku.

393
01:19:47,908 --> 01:19:49,576
Aku bersalah.

394
01:19:50,995 --> 01:19:52,121
Kumohon tolong aku.

395
01:20:35,789 --> 01:20:37,082
Ashin, kau kembali!

396
01:20:39,752 --> 01:20:40,753
Ya.

397
01:20:42,296 --> 01:20:43,756
Aku kembali.

398
01:22:25,607 --> 01:22:27,359
Rupanya kalian tidak makan apa-apa.

399
01:22:28,110 --> 01:22:29,820
Sudah kubilang jangan begitu.

400
01:23:06,064 --> 01:23:08,984
Tampaknya selama ini
caraku merawat kalian salah.

401
01:23:13,739 --> 01:23:15,532
Burung pegar, rusa, kelinci.

402
01:23:16,909 --> 01:23:18,827
Bukan itu yang kalian mau, 'kan?

403
01:23:52,569 --> 01:23:54,154
Mulai sekarang…

404
01:23:56,823 --> 01:23:59,201
akan kujamu kalian dengan makanan lezat.

405
01:24:06,625 --> 01:24:07,876
Ashin!

406
01:24:09,962 --> 01:24:12,714
Ashin!

407
01:24:19,304 --> 01:24:20,389
Ashin!

408
01:24:21,473 --> 01:24:22,641
Tidak!

409
01:24:25,644 --> 01:24:26,895
Ashin!

410
01:25:08,270 --> 01:25:09,146
Bagaimana?

411
01:25:42,012 --> 01:25:43,180
<i>Aku tidak kesepian.</i>

412
01:25:44,723 --> 01:25:47,059
<i>Aku tidak kesepian karena ada kalian.</i>

413
01:25:49,061 --> 01:25:50,687
<i>Setelah menyelesaikan semuanya,</i>

414
01:25:51,855 --> 01:25:55,484
<i>dan membunuh semua orang
yang ada di tanah Joseon dan Jurchen,</i>

415
01:25:56,777 --> 01:25:58,612
<i>aku pun akan mendampingi kalian.</i>

416
01:26:08,080 --> 01:26:12,709
PERBATASAN JOSEON, UIJU

417
01:26:12,793 --> 01:26:14,711
Kudengar ada perang lagi di selatan, ya?

418
01:26:15,295 --> 01:26:17,089
Jangan-jangan akan sampai ke sini.

419
01:26:17,923 --> 01:26:20,884
Barisan utusan Raja pun pergi ke Tiongkok
demi minta bala bantuan.

420
01:26:23,345 --> 01:26:26,556
Bila Tiongkok mau membantu,
kurasa kita takkan habis tak berdaya lagi.

421
01:26:29,059 --> 01:26:32,896
Ada barisan utusan Raja!

422
01:27:07,514 --> 01:27:08,849
Apa tanaman ini…

423
01:27:08,932 --> 01:27:10,642
TABIB LEE SEUNG-HUI

424
01:27:10,726 --> 01:27:13,478
sungguh dapat membangkitkan orang mati?

425
01:27:14,146 --> 01:27:15,397
Benar, Tuan.

426
01:27:16,857 --> 01:27:18,692
<i>Sebelum jasad mulai membusuk,</i>

427
01:27:19,568 --> 01:27:21,903
<i>tanaman itu dihaluskan, diberi air liur,</i>

428
01:27:23,238 --> 01:27:25,824
<i>kemudian ditusuk di titik</i> Yintang
<i>sedalam tiga milimeter.</i>

429
01:27:31,329 --> 01:27:34,666
Maka, mayat dapat hidup kembali
dua jam kemudian.

